valid = []
valid.append('2-2,2-4,2-5,2-6')
valid.append('4-2,4-4,4-5,4-6')
actual = self.runner('-r 2:5', '-R 3', '-c 2,4:7', None, options=
    "--delimiter=',' --quoting=quote_none")
assert valid == actual
actual = self.runner('-r 2,4', None, '-c 2,4,5,6', None, options=
    "--delimiter=',' --quoting=quote_none")
assert valid == actual
